dict.string: This is just a sample. Do NOT try loading it.

In most cases recommended to use Sample.plist
Use SampleFull.plist for end of life models: 2011 and older.
Fake ethernet card, work with NullEthernet, please disabled it if you have compatible wifi card
PNLF: Rename PNLF to XNLF to Fix Conflict with SSDT PNLF -> Fix boot win failed due to PNLF
GPIO: change _STA to XSTA in device GPI0 (TouchPad I2C)
I2C1: _STA to XSTA ,pair with SSDT-I2C.aml -> Touchpad fix
PTSWAK: Rename method _PTS to ZPTS and use with SSDT-PTSWAK.aml to fix dGPU power sapping
PTSWAK: Rename method _WAK to ZWAK and use with SSDT-PTSWAK.aml to fix dGPU power sapping
BRT6: Rename BRT6 to XRT6(dell) -> fix brightness key
ECDV: Changes ECDV to EC, fix boot in Catalina
GPRW to XPRW -> Fix instant wake
UPRW to XPRW -> Fix instant wake
Haswell: SB_RCBA is a 0x4 page memory region, containing SPI_BASE at 0x3800 (SPI_BASE_ADDRESS)
Generic: PCI root is a 0x1000 page memory region used by some firmwares
